data.Name: getuserbycontractnumber
data.Query:
SELECT (
    SELECT 
        u.Id AS id,
        u.ChannelId AS channelid,
        u.UserId AS userid,
        u.UserName AS username,
        u.UserCode AS usercode,
        u.LoginName AS loginname,
        u.FirstName AS firstname,
        u.MiddleName AS middlename,
        u.LastName AS lastname,
        u.RoleChannel AS rolechannel,
        u.Gender AS gender,
        u.Address AS address,
        u.Email AS email,
        u.Birthday AS birthday,
        u.Status AS status,
				[dbo].__GET_SYSTEM_CODE_CAPTION(u.STATUS, 'USERSTATUS', 'BO') AS statuscaption,
        u.UserCreated AS usercreated,
        u.LastLoginTime AS lastlogintime,
        u.UserModified AS usermodified,
        u.IsLogin AS islogin,
        u.ExpireTime AS expiretime,
        u.BranchID AS branchid,
        u.DepartmentCode AS departmentcode,
        u.UserLevel AS userlevel,
        u.UserType AS usertype,
        u.IsShow AS isshow,
        u.PolicyID AS policyid,
        u.UUID AS uuid,
        u.Failnumber AS failnumber,
        u.IsSuperAdmin AS issuperadmin,
        u.UpdatedOnUtc AS updatedonutc,
        u.CreatedOnUtc AS createdonutc,
        u.Phone AS phone,
        u.ContractNumber AS contractnumber
    FROM 
        o24cth.dbo.UserAccount u
    WHERE 
        u.ContractNumber = @id

) AS Result;

data.Name: SimpleSearchLoginDeviceInformation
data.Query:
SELECT 
    (SELECT A.ID AS id,
            A.UserCode AS usercode, 
            A.DeviceId AS deviceid,
            A.DeviceType AS devicetype,
            A.Status AS status, 
            A.PushId AS pushid,
            A.OsVersion AS osversion, 
            A.Brand AS brand, 
            A.LastSeenDateUtc  AS lastseenupdate,
            COUNT(*) OVER () AS TotalCount
     FROM 
         o24cth.dbo.UserDevice A
     WHERE 
         @searchtext IS NULL OR @searchtext = '' 
         OR A.UserCode LIKE '%' + @searchtext + '%'
     ORDER BY A.ID 
     OFFSET @Offset ROWS
     FETCH NEXT @PageSize ROWS ONLY
     FOR JSON PATH
) AS Result;

data.Name: SimpleSearchUser
data.Query:
WITH Filtered AS (
    SELECT *
    FROM dbo.UserAccount A
    WHERE 
        A.ChannelId = @channel
        AND (
            @searchtext IS NULL OR LTRIM(RTRIM(@searchtext)) = ''
            OR A.UserName LIKE '%' + @searchtext + '%'
            OR A.UserCode LIKE '%' + @searchtext + '%'
            OR A.LoginName LIKE '%' + @searchtext + '%'
            OR A.FirstName LIKE '%' + @searchtext + '%'
            OR A.MiddleName LIKE '%' + @searchtext + '%'
            OR A.LastName LIKE '%' + @searchtext + '%'
            OR A.Email LIKE '%' + @searchtext + '%'
            OR A.Phone LIKE '%' + @searchtext + '%'
        )
)
SELECT (
    SELECT 
        A.Id AS id,
        A.ChannelId AS channelid,
        A.UserId AS userid,
        A.UserName AS username,
        A.UserCode AS usercode,
        A.LoginName AS loginname,
        A.FirstName AS firstname,
        A.MiddleName AS middlename,
        A.LastName AS lastname,
        A.RoleChannel AS rolechannel,
        A.Gender AS gender,
        A.Address AS address,
        A.Email AS email,
        A.Birthday AS birthday,
        A.Status as status,
        A.UserCreated AS usercreated,
        A.LastLoginTime AS lastlogintime,
        A.UserModified AS usermodified,
        A.IsLogin AS islogin,
        A.ExpireTime AS expiretime,
        A.BranchID AS branchid,
        A.DepartmentCode AS departmentcode,
        A.UserLevel AS userlevel,
        A.UserType AS usertype,
        A.IsShow AS isshow,
        A.PolicyID AS policyid,
        A.UUID AS uuid,
        A.Failnumber AS failnumber,
        A.IsSuperAdmin AS issuperadmin,
        A.UpdatedOnUtc AS updatedonutc,
        A.CreatedOnUtc AS createdonutc,
        A.Phone AS phone,
        A.ContractNumber AS contractnumber,
        A.IsBiometricSupported AS isbiometricsupported,
        A.LockedUntil AS lockeduntil,
        COUNT(*) OVER () AS TotalCount
    FROM Filtered A
    ORDER BY A.ID
    OFFSET @Offset ROWS
    FETCH NEXT @PageSize ROWS ONLY
    FOR JSON PATH
) AS Result
OPTION (RECOMPILE);

data.Name: userview
data.Query:
SELECT (
    SELECT 
        u.Id AS id,
        u.ChannelId AS channelid,
        u.UserId AS userid,
        u.UserName AS username,
        u.UserCode AS usercode,
        u.LoginName AS loginname,
        u.FirstName AS firstname,
        u.MiddleName AS middlename,
        u.LastName AS lastname,
        u.RoleChannel AS rolechannel,
        CASE WHEN u.Gender = 1 THEN 'M' ELSE 'F' END AS gender,
        u.Address AS address,
        u.Email AS email,
        u.Birthday AS birthday,
        u.Status AS status,
				[dbo].__GET_SYSTEM_CODE_CAPTION(u.STATUS, 'USERSTATUS', 'BO') AS statuscaption,
        u.UserCreated AS usercreated,
        u.LastLoginTime AS lastlogintime,
        u.UserModified AS usermodified,
        u.IsLogin AS islogin,
        u.ExpireTime AS expiretime,
        u.BranchID AS branchid,
        u.DepartmentCode AS departmentcode,
        CAST(u.UserLevel AS NVARCHAR) AS userlevel,
        u.UserType AS usertype,
        u.IsShow AS isshow,
        u.PolicyID AS policyid,
        u.UUID AS uuid,
        u.Failnumber AS failnumber,
        u.IsSuperAdmin AS issuperadmin,
        u.UpdatedOnUtc AS updatedonutc,
        u.CreatedOnUtc AS createdonutc,
        u.Phone AS phone,
        u.ContractNumber AS contractnumber,
				(
						SELECT 
								r.[RoleName] AS [rolename],
								r.[RoleID] AS [roleid]
						FROM dbo.UserInRole ur
						INNER JOIN dbo.UserRole r ON ur.RoleID = r.RoleID
						WHERE ur.UserCode = u.UserCode
						ORDER BY r.roleid
						FOR JSON PATH
				) AS [usergroup]
    FROM 
        o24cth.dbo.UserAccount u
     
    WHERE 
    (
        TRY_CAST(@id AS INT) IS NOT NULL AND u.Id = TRY_CAST(@id AS INT)
    )
    OR (
        TRY_CAST(@id AS INT) IS NULL AND u.UserCode = @id
    )

    FOR JSON PATH, WITHOUT_ARRAY_WRAPPER
) AS Result;

data.Name: SimpleSearchUserSession

        U.Reference AS reference,

        U.ExpiresAt AS expiresat,

        U.ChannelId AS channelid,

        U.UpdatedOnUtc AS updatedonutc,

        @searchtext IS NULL OR @searchtext = ''
        OR U.LoginName LIKE '%' + @searchtext + '%'
        OR U.UserName LIKE '%' + @searchtext + '%'
        OR U.UserCode LIKE '%' + @searchtext + '%'
        OR U.IpAddress LIKE '%' + @searchtext + '%'
        OR U.Device LIKE '%' + @searchtext + '%'
				) AND u.ChannelId = @channel
    ORDER BY U.CreatedOnUtc DESC
    OFFSET @Offset ROWS
    FETCH NEXT @PageSize ROWS ONLY
    FOR JSON PATH
) AS Result;

        R.RoleDescription AS roledescription,
        R.UserType AS usertype,

data.Name: GetDbFunctions
data.Query:
SELECT
    SCHEMA_NAME(o.schema_id) COLLATE DATABASE_DEFAULT + '.' + o.[name] COLLATE DATABASE_DEFAULT AS [ObjectName],
    CASE o.[type]
        WHEN 'P' THEN 'Stored Procedure'
        WHEN 'FN' THEN 'Scalar Function'
        WHEN 'TF' THEN 'Table Function'
        WHEN 'IF' THEN 'Inline Table Function'
    END AS [ObjectType],
    'USE O24CMS' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) +
    'GO' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) +
    'IF OBJECT_ID(''' + SCHEMA_NAME(o.schema_id) COLLATE DATABASE_DEFAULT + '.' +
    o.[name] COLLATE DATABASE_DEFAULT + ''', ''' + o.[type] COLLATE DATABASE_DEFAULT + ''') IS NOT NULL ' +
    'DROP ' +
    CASE o.[type]
        WHEN 'P' THEN 'PROCEDURE '
        WHEN 'FN' THEN 'FUNCTION '
        WHEN 'TF' THEN 'FUNCTION '
        WHEN 'IF' THEN 'FUNCTION '
    END +
    SCHEMA_NAME(o.schema_id) COLLATE DATABASE_DEFAULT + '.' +
    o.[name] COLLATE DATABASE_DEFAULT + ';' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) +
    'GO' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) +
    m.[definition] COLLATE DATABASE_DEFAULT + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) +
    'GO' AS [Script]
FROM
    sys.sql_modules m
INNER JOIN
    sys.objects o ON m.object_id = o.object_id
WHERE
    o.[type] IN ('P', 'FN', 'TF', 'IF')
    AND SCHEMA_NAME(o.schema_id) = 'dbo'
ORDER BY
    o.[type], o.[name];
